    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and carefully maintained, so it\u2019s super clean and ready to hit the road with its next owner. If you\u2019re looking for a solid vehicle that feels great to drive, you\u2019ve found it. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014I'd love to chat!",
