    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a double VANOS high-pressure stepless variable valve timing system to deliver a linear power band peaking at its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain features a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission paired with a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock for optimal power delivery through the rear axles. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve lash adjustment and a thorough inspection of the rear subframe reinforcement points. The chassis retains its factory-tuned kinematics, offering precise turn-in and high-speed stability. This is a well-sorted example of BMW M's naturally aspirated peak, ready for the enthusiast who values tactile feedback and engineering purity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Regular maintenance records available. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear only. Runs well.",
      "price": 28500.0,
