    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold for me. This car is in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a dependable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I've stayed on top of the maintenance, so it's ready to hit the pavement with a new owner today. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
